1186
01:23:05,530 --> 01:23:07,464
Give them the vase.

1187
01:23:15,764 --> 01:23:17,629
Boss said I start shooting now.

1188
01:23:22,330 --> 01:23:23,991
Get in the truck.

1189
01:23:27,697 --> 01:23:29,289
Nobody goes anywhere.

1190
01:23:30,697 --> 01:23:31,994
Floss...

1191
01:23:32,197 --> 01:23:33,858
...fetch me that vase, please.

1192
01:23:34,063 --> 01:23:35,087
Get in the truck.

1193
01:23:35,530 --> 01:23:39,159
Give me the blood of Heracles, now.

1194
01:23:39,364 --> 01:23:40,626
Walk.

1195
01:23:40,830 --> 01:23:41,888
Heracles?

1196
01:23:44,297 --> 01:23:46,629
I always thought it was "Hercules."

1197
01:23:47,896 --> 01:23:49,523
You.

1198
01:24:09,930 --> 01:24:13,058
Sand, you found your armor.

1199
01:24:13,263 --> 01:24:14,560
Use it.

1200
01:24:14,764 --> 01:24:16,129
What is it with you and women?

1201
01:24:19,996 --> 01:24:21,827
Octopus...

1202
01:24:22,030 --> 01:24:23,793
...you were right.

1203
01:24:23,996 --> 01:24:25,588
We're mistakes.

1204
01:24:25,796 --> 01:24:27,388
We never should have happened.

1205
01:24:39,697 --> 01:24:41,665
- Sir, this is crazy.
- Hold your horses.

1206
01:24:41,863 --> 01:24:44,161
He doesn't want any cops
getting killed.

1207
01:24:48,397 --> 01:24:50,991
You're not making this easy.

1208
01:24:58,364 --> 01:24:59,490
Come on, kid.

1209
01:25:09,530 --> 01:25:11,259
It ends tonight.

1210
01:25:12,830 --> 01:25:14,092
You got that right.

1211
01:25:14,564 --> 01:25:16,225
I'm The Octopus.

1212
01:25:16,430 --> 01:25:17,795
I got eight of everything.

1213
01:25:40,464 --> 01:25:42,557
There's shot to hell.

1214
01:25:42,763 --> 01:25:44,390
And shot to hell.

1215
01:25:45,130 --> 01:25:47,928
And there's just plain ridiculous.

1216
01:25:48,397 --> 01:25:50,194
Now.

1217
01:26:10,364 --> 01:26:11,922
You idiot, Octopus.

1218
01:26:12,130 --> 01:26:15,622
All we needed was to flush you
and your gunsels out.

1219
01:26:19,664 --> 01:26:21,325
Move, move.

1220
01:26:26,863 --> 01:26:28,262
Give it to him, boys.

1221
01:27:29,330 --> 01:27:31,161
Commissioner Dolan,
your daughter's here.

1222
01:27:32,830 --> 01:27:34,092
We need more men over there.

1223
01:27:34,297 --> 01:27:37,061
- Baby, you don't wanna be here.
- You're joking, right, Daddy?

1224
01:27:37,263 --> 01:27:39,993
Have you forgotten what I do
for a living? He might need me.

1225
01:27:40,197 --> 01:27:42,427
You'll be in his way,
he doesn't want you here.

1226
01:27:42,630 --> 01:27:43,790
You don't know that.

1227
01:27:43,996 --> 01:27:47,295
You don't know him.
You don't know a damn thing.

1228
01:27:47,497 --> 01:27:49,260
Stop her. Pull her back.

1229
01:27:49,630 --> 01:27:50,722
Yes, sir.

1230
01:27:56,464 --> 01:27:58,295
Runny eggs.

1231
01:28:10,530 --> 01:28:13,021
Finally. Yes.

1232
01:28:13,230 --> 01:28:14,254
Yes.

1233
01:28:14,464 --> 01:28:18,195
Yeah!

1234
01:28:27,530 --> 01:28:28,895
Wha...?

1235
01:28:34,597 --> 01:28:36,622
Nice investment, Sand.

1236
01:28:36,830 --> 01:28:38,422
Passes its first field test.

1237
01:28:45,996 --> 01:28:47,224
Let's die.

1238
01:28:57,596 --> 01:28:59,723
Oh, God. Oh, God, no.

1239
01:29:00,596 --> 01:29:02,086
No. Oh, God.

1240
01:29:04,263 --> 01:29:05,594
Mother.

1241
01:29:32,963 --> 01:29:35,454
I guess it's time
to finally drop your armor, Sand.

1242
01:29:39,896 --> 01:29:41,989
You lost something.

1243
01:29:45,763 --> 01:29:48,163
Old man Kurtzman said
he'd take it back.

1244
01:29:53,629 --> 01:29:55,062
Well...

1245
01:29:56,063 --> 01:29:58,088
...maybe I'll wear it now and then.

1246
01:29:58,297 --> 01:30:00,561
But it doesn't mean I'm your girl.

1247
01:30:39,197 --> 01:30:41,961
Ellen. Ellen, are you all right?

1248
01:31:12,163 --> 01:31:13,391
Goodbye, Sand.

1249
01:31:14,863 --> 01:31:16,626
Goodbye, Denny.

1250
01:31:40,730 --> 01:31:42,527
Goodbye, Spirit.

1251
01:31:46,097 --> 01:31:47,997
- Is that Saref?
- Give me this one, Dolan.

1252
01:31:48,197 --> 01:31:49,425
Just let her go.

1253
01:31:49,629 --> 01:31:52,325
She saved me.
She saved the world.

1254
01:31:52,529 --> 01:31:55,692
Yeah, well,
you had something to do with it.

1255
01:31:55,896 --> 01:31:58,364
All right. All right.
Just stay out of my face.

1256
01:32:04,197 --> 01:32:06,791
So who the hell was that back there?
Who is she?

1257
01:32:06,996 --> 01:32:08,258
Just an old flame.

1258
01:32:08,464 --> 01:32:10,432
Yeah, she looks old.

1259
01:32:10,629 --> 01:32:13,393
- It's you I love, baby. With all my heart.
- Yeah.

1260
01:32:13,596 --> 01:32:15,860
Me and every other woman
you meet.

1261
01:32:17,163 --> 01:32:19,631
You are amazing.

1262
01:32:19,830 --> 01:32:21,422
Neat work yourself, rookie.

1263
01:32:23,863 --> 01:32:25,763
Bastard.

1264
01:32:50,596 --> 01:32:52,962
We start from scratch.

1265
01:33:02,230 --> 01:33:04,460
Who knows what I'll do?

1266
01:33:12,197 --> 01:33:15,394
<i>She wakes. Grouchy as always.</i>

1267
01:33:16,629 --> 01:33:18,597
<i>Endlessly noisy.</i>

1268
01:33:19,596 --> 01:33:21,962
<i>Endlessly alive.</i>

1269
01:33:22,930 --> 01:33:25,364
<i>She's all I really have.</i>

1270
01:33:25,996 --> 01:33:28,260
<i>My only hope.</i>

1271
01:33:29,063 --> 01:33:31,258
<i>My only constant.</i>

1272
01:33:32,996 --> 01:33:35,396
<i>The secrets of The Octopus
died with him.</i>

1273
01:33:38,097 --> 01:33:40,224
<i>I don't know what I am
or how long I got.</i>

1274
01:33:40,429 --> 01:33:42,624
<i>Heck, maybe I'll live forever.</i>

1275
01:33:42,830 --> 01:33:44,354
<i>I hope not.</i>

1276
01:33:44,563 --> 01:33:46,428
<i>That's nothing any man
ought to have.</i>

1277
01:33:46,629 --> 01:33:49,063
<i>That's nothing any man
ought to want.</i>

1278
01:33:49,429 --> 01:33:52,227
<i>Denny Colt is dead.
I'm something else now...</i>

1279
01:33:52,429 --> 01:33:55,364
<i>... and I can never give my heart
to anyone but her.</i>

1280
01:33:55,563 --> 01:33:59,226
<i>She will always be mine
and I will always be hers.</i>

1281
01:33:59,429 --> 01:34:02,125
<i>She owns me, body and soul.</i>

1282
01:34:02,330 --> 01:34:04,924
<i>She is the love of my life.</i>

1283
01:34:05,529 --> 01:34:07,793
<i>She is my city.</i>

1284
01:34:09,796 --> 01:34:11,593
<i>And I...</i>

1285
01:34:11,896 --> 01:34:14,126
<i>... am her Spirit.</i>

